text: Richard Nutt (25 June 1911 - 5 February 1985) was an Australian cricketer. He played six first-class matches for New South Wales between 1931/32 and 1932/33. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1911 births Category:1985 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
